					</section>


					<section id="organizer" class="two">
						<div class="container">

							<header>
								<h2>YOUR ORGANIZERS</h2>
							</header>

							<p>Our names are Jeniveve Pearson and Jasmin Washington, we are 3rd year graduate students at Steward. This year, we are running the prospective visit. We hope this visit can give you a comprehensive preview of the science from our department and what it’s like to live in Tucson, AZ as a grad student. Spoiler, it's pretty rad! If you need to get in touch with us, shoot us an email or send us a Slack message.  
							</p>

							<ul>
								<li>Jeniveve Pearson: &ensp;<a href="mailto:jenivevepearson@arizona.edu">jenivevepearson@arizona.edu</a></li>
